{"tid":687923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位軍師獻計","createTime":"2018-06-02T17:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T17:38:24.000Z","uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3619e014c49a62b7f6ba3896aa4245188cc90272","tid":687923,"uid":77132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"行動計劃<br />\n報復前女朋友<br />\n而家分開咗一個月佢完完全全唔care但係我係佢咁多男朋友入邊係最長嗰個同埋係最有feel<br />\n佢而家都係周圍搵人做水泡從來拍拖冇認真過<br />\n我打算過多一排追番佢去到某個時候同佢講分手俾佢感受下係乜嘢滋味<br />\n請各位巴打獻計首先而家第一步要點做<br />\n我而家打算靜觀其變等佢係最失意嘅時候 乘虛而入<br />\n然後狠狠咁溝咗佢之後係大家愛得最深嘅時候再飛咗佢。<br />\n首先我想各位巴打依家教我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050f1928a2359165ddbf9684b346917e37404c8a","tid":687923,"uid":88797,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"有時間增值自己 搵一個更好 無需要浪費時間報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3a92e8bc39abae9a9aa0cbd2b992e0a143b621","tid":687923,"uid":90605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"哂氣"},{"pid":"ac24fa203752f3d1757489ab76524437cd73f18b","tid":687923,"uid":77132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"050f1928a2359165ddbf9684b346917e37404c8a","tid":687923,"uid":88797,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"有時間增值自己 搵一個更好 無需要浪費時間報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"唔好意思我一定要玩到好盡<br />\n玩到佢到時自殺都要我都唔會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227720855f3f6a80d16055ed79744f1981e2c763","tid":687923,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:11:52.000Z","msg":"say sorry話請佢食啲好撚貴既高級野<br />\n食到一半話去洗手間 之後你明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e6025e5e09c50d47a9fe3dd12